Package: iarm
Type: Package
Title: Item analysis in Rasch Models
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Marianne", "Mueller", email = "mllm@zhaw.ch", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Tools to assess model fit and identify misfitting items for Rasch models (RM) and partial credit models (PCM). Included are item fit statistics, item-restscore association, conditional likelihood ratio tests, assessment of measurement error, reliability and targeting.
License: GPL-2
Depends: R (>= 3.3.2), eRm
Imports:
    PP,
    psychotools
Suggests:
    testthat
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
